        },
        "subject": "LU-5030 utils: create llapi_{get,set}_param function",
        "message": "LU-5030 utils: create llapi_{get,set}_param function\n\nAbstract out {get,set}_param pathname generation so that it is\ncommon between the different parts of liblustreapi by creating\nnew functions called llapi_{get,set}_param. This reduces code\nduplication as well as simplifies changes to the /proc\nparameter location in the future.\n\nChange-Id: I6a33ba82fcb40cbc4631c30cab7ac668adb79c45\nSigned-off-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nSigned-off-by: Chao Wang <chao.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
